---

## How to Use This Index

Each section links to a section hub that lists its notes with keywords. Navigate to the section relevant to your task, then drill into the specific notes you need.

### Always Read First

These notes are **required reading** for every task, regardless of which section you're working in. They define the patterns everything else builds on:

1. **[[your-conventions-note]]** â€” Add your naming, function ordering, and code hygiene conventions here.
2. **[[your-folder-structure-note]]** â€” Add your folder layout and progressive disclosure conventions here.

---

